|根拠地={{ill|Echigo Province|ja|越後国}} {{ill|Kanbara District|ja|蒲原郡}} {{ill|Sawakami Village|ja|沢海村}}<br>{{ill|Iwashiro District|ja|岩船郡}} {{ill|Murakami|ja|村上市}}<br>{{ill|Dewa Province|ja|出羽国}} {{ill|Akumi District|ja|飽海郡}} {{ill|Sakata, Yamagata|ja|酒田市}}<br>{{ill|Tagawa District|ja|田川郡 (羽前国)}} {{ill|Tsuruoka|ja|鶴岡市}}
|人物={{ill|Kazama Nobuaki|ja|風間信昭}}<br>{{ill|Kazama Shinichi|ja|風間眞一}} {{ill|Kazama Kazuki|ja|風間一輝}}
